Wordle Buddy bugs and fixes 3/13/2022

>Sometimes after 3-4 guesses that mostly result in grey letters, Wordle Buddy will get confused and suggest nothing. 
Example being today, my first 3 guesses resulted in almost all grey letters. Despite my next guess being mostly green, the program suggested nothing.

=Restart program and enter in your recent guesses. This kicks him back into gear. Solved it after one guess.







Wordle Buddy fun facts:

>It seems the first suggestion the program gives is normally the correct anwser. Need to compile more runs to get the average.
